  <h3>
    First session
  </h3>
  <p>
    In the first session of the game, the players will create their explorers
    and play through the first scenario created by the Keeper. Some of the
    explorer creation can be done ahead of time, but it's best to collaborate
    and make sure that your team makes sense for the type of game you want to
    play.
  </p>
  <p>
    Before the first session, players may choose their archetypes and fill out
    their dossiers up to the Introductions section, or you may want to do the
    whole explorer creation process during the first session. The choice is
    yours, but the Introductions and History sections need to be filled out
    collaboratively. Each player will describe their explorer and choose options
    that inform the relationships between them and the other explorers.
  </p>
