  <h4>
    Custom archetypes
  </h4>
  <p>
    You don't need to stick to this list of archetypes if you have a cool idea.
    Talk to your Keeper, and see if you can work together to create a new
    archetype that would be a good fit for your game. You can decide what
    special moves, gear, or other traits that the explorer should have, as long
    as it fits loosely with the rules of the game.
  </p>
